                <li>Reviewing the full application to ensure compliance with Immigration New Zealand policy</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Result:</strong> The residence visa was approved for Mr. Ma, his partner, and their child in 2 and half months. The family is now happily settling in Auckland.</p>
